Introduction

Huang Xingqiao, also known as Lorina, is a Chinese singer signed with Origin Music International and Panda Record (Japan). She debuted as a soloist on November 3, 2017, with the single “Seventeen Years Old.”

She was a participant in the hit survival show, Girls Planet 999 and the Chinese reality survival show The Coming One 3.
